---
---

<section class="py-16 bg-white relative">
  <!-- Background Pattern -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#145da0 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-ultimate-blue/10 border border-ultimate-blue/20 text-ultimate-blue text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Keunggulan Kami</span>
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl text-ultimate-navy mb-6">
        Mengapa Memilih <span class="text-ultimate-blue">Ultimate Education?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Kami menggabungkan metode pembelajaran teruji, mentor berkualitas internasional, dan dukungan personal untuk memastikan kesuksesan studi Anda.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      {/* Point 1 - Garansi Skor */}
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-ultimate-blue transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-ultimate-blue group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-heading text-ultimate-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-ultimate-blue transition-colors">Jaminan Kualitas</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Program garansi mengulang kelas GRATIS jika target skor IELTS/TOEFL/SAT Anda belum tercapai. Investasi pendidikan yang aman dan terjamin.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Point 2 - Mentor Top Dunia */}
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-yellow-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-ultimate-yellow transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600 group-hover:text-ultimate-navy transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 00-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0112 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 018.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 00-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 00-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0112 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0110.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0112 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 017.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0112 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 006.75 15.75v-1.5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-heading text-ultimate-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-ultimate-blue transition-colors">Mentor Expert</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Belajar langsung dari Native Speaker dan alumni universitas top dunia (Ivy League, UK Russell Group) dengan skor tes tinggi.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Point 3 - Curriculum Terbaik */}
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-green-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-heading text-ultimate-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-ultimate-blue transition-colors">Kurikulum Terupdate</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Materi pembelajaran disusun sistematis sesuai standar tes internasional terbaru, fokus pada strategi pengerjaan soal yang efektif.
        </p>
      </div>

      {/* Point 4 - Full Support */}
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors duration-300">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-heading text-ultimate-navy mb-3 group-hover:text-ultimate-blue transition-colors">Support Lengkap</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Pendampingan end-to-end mulai dari simulasi tes (mock test), review essay, hingga simulasi interview beasiswa dan universitas.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
